## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="2d573-123">以下示例对语音识别语法，执行异步语音识别使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizeAsync%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>与进程内识别器的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d573-123">The following example performs asynchronous speech recognition on a speech recognition grammar, using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizeAsync%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method with the in-process recognizer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2d573-124">该示例使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices>并<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>对象生成到前创建语音识别语法<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d573-124">The example uses <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects to create the speech recognition grammar before building it into a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2d573-125">处理程序<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizeCompleted?displayProperty=nameWithType>事件输出到控制台的识别操作的相关信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d573-125">A handler for the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizeCompleted?displayProperty=nameWithType> event outputs information about the recognition operation to the console.</span></span>  
  
